            + `add_to_price` (object) - Default (to all options) price alteration if customer use this field
                + `type`: percentage (enum) - Type of price addition
                    + `percentage` (string)
                    + `fixed` (string)
                + `addition` (number, required) - Additional value, could be negative - Mininum: **-99999999** - Maximum: **99999999** - Max precision: **0.0001**
