### All Products [/products.json{?sku}]

*/products.json?sku*

> Authentication<br>_GET_: **none**

Pagination is not available, the unique possible filter is by `sku`

Returns only `_id` and `sku` of each product

#### List All Store Products [GET /products.json]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            X-Store-ID: 100

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "meta": {
                "query": {}
              },
              "result": [
                {
                  "_id": "1234567890abcdef01291510",
                  "sku": "COD1"
                },
                {
                  "_id": "1234567890abcdef01291511",
                  "sku": "S_123456789"
                },
                {
                  "_id": "1234567890abcdef01291512",
                  "sku": "sYY7-100P"
                }
              ]
            }

#### Find Product [GET]

+ Parameters
    + sku: COD1 (string, optional) - The product SKU

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            X-Store-ID: 100

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "meta": {
                "query": {
                  "sku": "COD1"
                }
              },
              "result": [
                {
                  "_id": "1234567890abcdef01291510",
                  "sku": "COD1"
                }
              ]
            }

